) AS [t]

    SELECT [i6].[ID], [i6].[CreatedBy], [i6].[CreatedDate], [i6].[FirstWeight], [i6].[IsActive], [i6].[IsRemoved], [i6].[ItemName], [i6].[LastModifiedBy], [i6].[LastModifiedDate], [i6].[Quantity], [i6].[Remarks], [i6].[SampleGatePassID], [i6].[SecondWeight], [i6].[UnitID]
